<scriptment id="36000" point="meguro" localizationstatus="original" fictionaldate="2011-07-20" status="final">
	<part>
		<narration>Passing by Yuki is a man on his phone.</narration>
		<line id="1000" speaker="meguro" voicelang="ja">...didn't "uphold to the critical standard set by previous entries?"</line>
		<line id="2000" speaker="meguro" voicelang="ja">An 8.5 on GameSpot?</line>
		<line id="3000" speaker="meguro" voicelang="ja">32/40 on Famitsu?</line>
		<line id="4000" speaker="meguro" voicelang="ja">Are you firing me because of mainstream video game journalism?</line>
		<narration>The man listens.</narration>
		<line id="5000" speaker="meguro" voicelang="ja">You can't fire a man who doesn't work for you.</line>
		<line id="6000" speaker="meguro" voicelang="ja">Or anyone else, for that matter.</line>
		<line id="7000" speaker="meguro" voicelang="ja">Good luck with your future Megatens.</line>
		<line id="8000" speaker="meguro" voicelang="ja">I quit.</line>
	</part>
</scriptment>
